Coding

A. Duplicate Code, to prevent is make the duplicate code into shared function to reduce repetitive and improve maintainability

B. Design pattern that aims to improve code modularity, flexibility, and testability by separating the creation of objects from their use. And benefits are, improve modularity, enchanced manntainability

Rest API

A. POST mostly using for creating new record, dont used POST to retrieve data, use GET

B. PUT used for updating existing record, dont used PUT to create new record, use POST

c. GET is used to list/show created record, dont use GET to modify or create record, use POST and PUT

